    {
      "id": 1,
      "title": "Meta 페이지 파트너 할당 가이드_EN",
      "excerpt": "[Video Guide]",
      "date": "2025-11-20",
      "views": 3241,
      "media": [],
      "steps": [
        {
          "text": "- Select the fan page to assign a partner.",
          "media": [
            {
              "url": "/uploads/1779430661344-kdym-pt_en_01-835x420.JPEG",
              "name": "pt_en_01-835x420.JPEG",
              "type": "image",
              "size": 93110,
              "width": null,
              "height": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "- Click the 'Assign Partner' option on the selected fan page.",
          "media": [
            {
              "url": "/uploads/1779430665890-ae1c-pt_en_02-835x420.JPEG",
              "name": "pt_en_02-835x420.JPEG",
              "type": "image",
              "size": 91619,
              "width": null,
              "height": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "- Click 'Business ID' in the partner assignment popup.",
          "media": [
            {
              "url": "/uploads/1779430673291-4fg7-pt_en_03-835x420.JPEG",
              "name": "pt_en_03-835x420.JPEG",
              "type": "image",
              "size": 67968,
              "width": null,
              "height": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "- Enter the Nasmedia Business ID (793587697339145) in the 'Enter partner business ID' field.\n- After entering the Business ID, grant the minimum permissions required for ad operations.\n(Required options: Content, Ads, Insights)\n- After selecting the permissions, click the 'Assign' button.",
          "media": [
            {
              "url": "/uploads/1779430678490-spxc-pt_en_04-835x420.JPEG",
              "name": "pt_en_04-835x420.JPEG",
              "type": "image",
              "size": 105352,
              "width": null,
              "height": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "- Check the 'Partner Assignment Complete' popup.",
          "media": [
            {
              "url": "/uploads/1779430682806-e3yb-pt_en_05-835x420.JPEG",
              "name": "pt_en_05-835x420.JPEG",
              "type": "image",
              "size": 65307,
              "width": null,
              "height": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "- Check the 'Partners' section of the fan page to confirm the assignment was successful.",
          "media": [
            {
              "url": "/uploads/1779430687681-90kt-pt_en_06-835x420.JPEG",
              "name": "pt_en_06-835x420.JPEG",
              "type": "image",
              "size": 88873,
              "width": null,
              "height": null
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "excerptMedia": [
        {
          "url": "/uploads/1779429298577-3lcz-pt_video_en1.mp4",
          "name": "pt_video_en1.mp4",
          "type": "video",
          "size": 6507233,
          "width": null,
          "height": null
        }
      ]
    },
    {
